WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-RO

00:00:06.097 --> 00:00:08.922
What is...what is the purpose of life,

00:00:08.922 --> 00:00:11.975
if you could give us some perspective?

00:00:11.975 --> 00:00:13.432
Thank you!  Is

00:00:19.282 --> 00:00:21.868
n't it fantastic that, having no purpose,

00:00:21.868 --> 00:00:22.884
having nothing to accomplish,

00:00:22.884 --> 00:00:24.427
you can just live?

00:00:26.057 --> 00:00:27.291
Hmm?

00:00:27.291 --> 00:00:27.860
No,

00:00:27.860 --> 00:00:30.064
you are asking for a purpose,

00:00:30.064 --> 00:00:34.350
and not just a simple purpose, but a Divine purpose.  It

00:00:34.350 --> 00:00:36.342
is very dangerous.

00:00:36.342 --> 00:00:38.762
People who believe they have a purpose set by God

00:00:38.762 --> 00:00:42.472
are responsible for the worst things on the planet.  Yes or no

00:00:42.472 --> 00:00:44.805
?

00:00:44.805 --> 00:00:47.101
They do the most horrible things

00:00:47.101 --> 00:00:50.435
and have always done the most horrible things

00:00:50.435 --> 00:00:53.505
because when you have a purpose from God,

00:00:53.505 --> 00:00:58.430
life becomes less important.

00:00:59.750 --> 00:01:00.353
No,

00:01:00.353 --> 00:01:02.810
life is important.

00:01:02.810 --> 00:01:04.324
Life is important.

00:01:04.324 --> 00:01:05.944
When I say life, I do

00:01:05.944 --> 00:01:12.060
n't mean your family life, your work, what you do, or what you don't do, your parties.  I do

00:01:12.060 --> 00:01:14.132
n't mean life in this sense.

00:01:14.132 --> 00:01:17.714
That's life, isn't it?

00:01:17.714 --> 00:01:20.476
Is life within you or around you?  The

00:01:22.186 --> 00:01:25.233
ambiance of life...

00:01:25.233 --> 00:01:28.872
you're confusing the ambiance of life with life.

00:01:28.872 --> 00:01:34.081
Your home, your family, your work, your party,

00:01:34.081 --> 00:01:36.342
this is the ambiance of your life.

00:01:36.342 --> 00:01:38.595
This isn't life, is it?  Yes or no

00:01:38.595 --> 00:01:39.559
?  Yes.

00:01:39.559 --> 00:01:40.582


00:01:40.582 --> 00:01:43.738
You are confusing the ambiance of life with real life.

00:01:43.738 --> 00:01:45.060
Not.

00:01:45.060 --> 00:01:47.458
Life is important

00:01:47.458 --> 00:01:49.469
because it is the only thing you know, you

00:01:49.469 --> 00:01:50.782
know nothing else.  Do

00:01:50.782 --> 00:01:53.427
you know anything else?

00:01:53.427 --> 00:01:55.468
The rest is just imagination, right?

00:01:55.468 --> 00:02:00.650
The only thing that pulsates and has life is this.

00:02:00.650 --> 00:02:02.277
So, is this important?  It

00:02:02.277 --> 00:02:04.998
is extremely important.

00:02:07.248 --> 00:02:10.970
Not you as a person, that's not what's important,

00:02:10.970 --> 00:02:12.643
but you as a part of life

00:02:12.643 --> 00:02:14.922
are very important

00:02:14.922 --> 00:02:17.352
because that's the foundation for everything.

00:02:17.352 --> 00:02:19.729
When I say that this is the foundation for everything, the

00:02:19.729 --> 00:02:24.097
universe exists for you only because you exist, right?  Yes or no

00:02:24.097 --> 00:02:25.865
?

00:02:25.865 --> 00:02:28.352
The world exists for you only because you exist,

00:02:28.352 --> 00:02:31.444
otherwise it would not exist in your experience.

00:02:31.444 --> 00:02:35.047
So, in all ways this is important.

00:02:35.047 --> 00:02:37.738
So, what is the purpose?

00:02:42.058 --> 00:02:45.288
You see, if you had a goal and you accomplished it,

00:02:45.288 --> 00:02:49.582
what else would you do?

00:02:49.582 --> 00:02:52.276
What are you doing next?

00:02:52.276 --> 00:02:54.159
Boredom, isn't it?  It's just

00:02:56.209 --> 00:03:02.161
that life is so complex and so phenomenally complicated

00:03:02.161 --> 00:03:07.087
that if you spent 10,000 years carefully analyzing it, you

00:03:07.087 --> 00:03:11.967
still wouldn't discover it in its entirety.

00:03:11.967 --> 00:03:16.951
If you spent a million years looking at her with absolute attention you

00:03:16.951 --> 00:03:20.092
still wouldn't know her completely.

00:03:20.092 --> 00:03:22.320
That's how things are.  Does it make

00:03:23.660 --> 00:03:26.142
sense?

00:03:26.142 --> 00:03:31.492
The most wonderful thing about life is that it has no meaning.

00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:35.602
This is the most significant aspect of life, namely that it has no meaning.

00:03:35.602 --> 00:03:39.280
and it doesn't even need a meaning.

00:03:39.282 --> 00:03:43.600
Only the small mind seeks meaning

00:03:43.602 --> 00:03:51.522
because on a psychological level you feel somehow disconnected from life

00:03:51.522 --> 00:03:54.362
if you don't have a purpose and meaning.

00:03:54.362 --> 00:03:59.272
People are always trying to create these false goals.

00:04:01.152 --> 00:04:04.496
So, they were somehow well and happy.

00:04:04.496 --> 00:04:05.759
Suddenly, they got married.

00:04:05.759 --> 00:04:10.349
Now the goal is the other person.

00:04:10.349 --> 00:04:11.758
Then they have children.

00:04:11.758 --> 00:04:14.164
Now they hate each other.

00:04:14.164 --> 00:04:18.112
Now the reason I endure suffering is children.

00:04:18.112 --> 00:04:20.212
In this way, we move forward.

00:04:21.582 --> 00:04:23.257
Are these things that you create

00:04:23.257 --> 00:04:26.974
and consider the purpose of life,

00:04:26.974 --> 00:04:30.336
and is there a purpose from God?  What

00:04:30.336 --> 00:04:34.589
if God doesn't know you exist?

00:04:34.589 --> 00:04:37.601
No, I'm just asking, randomly.  I'm just saying

00:04:41.351 --> 00:04:46.352
that, in this immense cosmos,

00:04:46.352 --> 00:04:49.528
where God is supposed to be the Creator

00:04:49.528 --> 00:04:53.181
and ruler of these hundreds of billions of galaxies,

00:04:53.181 --> 00:04:55.341
of which this little planet

00:04:55.341 --> 00:04:56.284
and you are a part...

00:04:56.284 --> 00:05:00.454
Suppose He doesn't know that you exist?

00:05:00.454 --> 00:05:02.564
Is it possible or not?

00:05:02.564 --> 00:05:05.530
Sorry, I'm saying so many sacrileges,

00:05:05.530 --> 00:05:08.194
but is it possible or not?  What

00:05:08.194 --> 00:05:10.768
if He doesn't know you exist?  What

00:05:13.578 --> 00:05:18.530
if he doesn't have a plan for you?

00:05:18.530 --> 00:05:20.998
Let's assume that He doesn't have a plan,

00:05:20.998 --> 00:05:24.308
a personal plan for you.

00:05:24.308 --> 00:05:27.182
Don't look for these things.

00:05:27.182 --> 00:05:31.818
Creation is made in such a way that

00:05:31.818 --> 00:05:34.847
Creation and Creator cannot be separated.

00:05:34.847 --> 00:05:36.842
Here you are a part of creation.

00:05:36.842 --> 00:05:41.524
At the same time, the source of creation pulsates within you.

00:05:41.524 --> 00:05:45.275
If you were a little more attentive to this process of life, you would

00:05:45.275 --> 00:05:46.973
n't need any goals.  It would keep

00:05:46.973 --> 00:05:50.377
you busy for a million years if you wanted to.

00:05:50.377 --> 00:05:52.048
So much happening

00:05:52.048 --> 00:05:57.225
so much means so many incredible things are happening right here.

00:05:57.225 --> 00:06:00.306
If you're careful enough,

00:06:00.306 --> 00:06:05.142
a million years of existence will keep you busy and beyond.

00:06:05.142 --> 00:06:07.632
At this moment, you need a purpose

00:06:07.632 --> 00:06:11.134
because you are stuck in your psychological structure,

00:06:11.134 --> 00:06:13.649
and not in the process of your life.

00:06:13.649 --> 00:06:15.787
From a psychological point of view,

00:06:15.787 --> 00:06:20.951
your psychological structure works with the limited information it has accumulated.  That's how it

00:06:20.951 --> 00:06:25.151
works now,

00:06:25.151 --> 00:06:30.782
thoughts and feelings have become more important than life.  Isn't that right?  Isn't that right

00:06:30.782 --> 00:06:32.325
?

00:06:32.325 --> 00:06:37.146
So, for this reason you are looking for a purpose through which to free yourself from the trap you

00:06:37.146 --> 00:06:41.086
have set for yourself.

00:06:41.086 --> 00:06:43.643
It is a trap of its own.

00:06:43.643 --> 00:06:46.678
You can easily get out of it.

00:06:46.678 --> 00:06:48.970
If the trap was set for you by someone else,

00:06:48.970 --> 00:06:50.434
it's more difficult to get out

00:06:50.434 --> 00:06:54.734
because they'll set the trap in such a way that you can't free yourself, right?

00:06:56.674 --> 00:06:58.726
I'm talking... I'm talking about life and not marriage, that's what I

00:06:58.726 --> 00:07:00.527
mean.  That's what

00:07:04.087 --> 00:07:06.758
I mean.

00:07:06.758 --> 00:07:09.520
So if it's a trap of its own.

00:07:09.520 --> 00:07:11.786
You get off easy,

00:07:11.786 --> 00:07:14.171
but that's the whole point.  The

00:07:14.171 --> 00:07:16.661
reason it's difficult

00:07:16.661 --> 00:07:19.194
is that you've become one with that trap, you

00:07:19.194 --> 00:07:21.006
like it.  You

00:07:21.006 --> 00:07:27.734
like it because it gives you a certain sense of

00:07:27.734 --> 00:07:33.339
safety and security and protection and individual identity.

00:07:33.339 --> 00:07:36.226
If you wrap yourself in a cocoon,

00:07:36.226 --> 00:07:37.778
you feel safe,

00:07:37.778 --> 00:07:40.611
but at the same time it imprisons you.

00:07:40.611 --> 00:07:46.502
Self-preserving walls are also self-imprisoning walls.

00:07:48.442 --> 00:07:50.665
When they protect you, you enjoy it.

00:07:50.665 --> 00:07:55.418
When they limit you, you don't enjoy it.  That's why

00:07:55.418 --> 00:07:57.911
we have doors.

00:07:57.911 --> 00:08:01.903
We like walls because they protect us,

00:08:01.903 --> 00:08:05.789
but we have doors so we can open them and get out when we want.

00:08:05.789 --> 00:08:10.753
No matter how nice it is, we still want to go out, right?  That's the way it is

00:08:10.753 --> 00:08:14.700
with any trap you set.

00:08:14.700 --> 00:08:18.686
No matter how nice it is, you still want to go out.

00:08:18.686 --> 00:08:21.632
So, the psychological wall that you have erected,

00:08:21.632 --> 00:08:24.133
which gives you some sense of identity,

00:08:24.133 --> 00:08:27.585
which gives you some sense that you are a person,

00:08:27.585 --> 00:08:32.925
a unique person, and which gives you security,

00:08:32.925 --> 00:08:34.873
starting to feel like a trap,

00:08:34.873 --> 00:08:37.449
somewhere you will want to break it.

00:08:37.449 --> 00:08:43.469
So, one way to not break it is to find a purpose.

00:08:43.469 --> 00:08:46.468
Those who find purpose in their lives,

00:08:46.468 --> 00:08:48.055
become so conceited... They

00:08:48.055 --> 00:08:50.904
will live in their own trap forever

00:08:50.904 --> 00:08:53.793
thinking they are doing the most fantastic thing.

00:08:53.793 --> 00:08:56.736
First you need balance.

00:08:56.736 --> 00:09:00.880
If you don't have balance, you can't climb.

00:09:00.880 --> 00:09:05.297
If you're off balance, you better stay down, right?  It

00:09:05.297 --> 00:09:10.360
's not safe for someone who is not balanced to climb to high altitudes.

00:09:10.360 --> 00:09:12.437
It's better to stay close to the ground.  You

00:09:12.437 --> 00:09:14.632
shouldn't go up.

00:09:14.632 --> 00:09:18.159
So, first establish a balance,

00:09:18.159 --> 00:09:21.683
then you weaken your psychological structure,

00:09:21.683 --> 00:09:23.165
then a wonderful thing happens.

00:09:23.165 --> 00:09:26.924
If you weaken your psychological structure without balance,

00:09:26.924 --> 00:09:29.542
which many people do today...

00:09:29.542 --> 00:09:32.725
See, why do some people want to consume alcohol and take drugs?

00:09:32.725 --> 00:09:38.601
Because you weaken your psychological structure and feel free for the moment.

00:09:38.601 --> 00:09:41.879
But without the necessary balance

00:09:41.879 --> 00:09:47.322
if you haven't worked to have balance, but you have been set free,

00:09:47.322 --> 00:09:53.091
freedom without balance is destruction, anarchy, isn't it?

00:09:53.091 --> 00:09:56.164
So, first you work for balance,

00:09:56.164 --> 00:09:58.498
a huge sense of balance,

00:09:58.498 --> 00:10:01.956
and even if you demolish your psychological structure,

00:10:01.956 --> 00:10:04.962
you can just live here.

00:10:04.962 --> 00:10:08.664
Demolishing the psychological structure is an important process

00:10:08.664 --> 00:10:10.974
because this is your trap,

00:10:10.974 --> 00:10:12.862
it is your safety, it

00:10:12.862 --> 00:10:14.601
is your stability

00:10:14.601 --> 00:10:17.439
and at the same time, it is your trap.

00:10:19.199 --> 00:10:25.199
Because of the walls, you feel safe, but it's a trap.

00:10:25.199 --> 00:10:28.962
If you destroy your trap,

00:10:28.962 --> 00:10:32.135
you also lose your safety, right?  You

00:10:32.135 --> 00:10:34.632
also lose your purpose.

00:10:34.632 --> 00:10:39.410
You lose everything that matters to you.

00:10:39.410 --> 00:10:41.468
So, that's why balance is needed.

00:10:41.468 --> 00:10:46.197
Without balance, if you destroy you will go crazy.

00:10:46.197 --> 00:10:48.819
But don't look for a goal,

00:10:48.819 --> 00:10:53.274
because if you're looking for a goal, you're looking for madness.

00:10:53.274 --> 00:10:57.181
If you find it, you are definitely crazy.  Yes.

00:10:59.111 --> 00:11:00.933


00:11:00.933 --> 00:11:03.342
If you think you've found the purpose of life, you've

00:11:03.342 --> 00:11:06.420
definitely gone crazy

00:11:08.440 --> 00:11:11.593
because only crazy people have a purpose,

00:11:11.593 --> 00:11:17.026
or people who have a purpose are crazy in many ways.

00:11:17.026 --> 00:11:19.342
These are things you create in your mind

00:11:19.342 --> 00:11:21.443
and believe are real, right?

00:11:21.443 --> 00:11:25.917
At this moment, "fighting for my country is my goal."

00:11:25.917 --> 00:11:33.932
At this moment, if necessary, I will fight, knowing full well that it is a bloody and useless fight.  Yes.

00:11:33.932 --> 00:11:34.975


00:11:34.975 --> 00:11:37.792
Then you will fight only as long as necessary.

00:11:37.792 --> 00:11:39.580
If you think that's your goal,

00:11:39.580 --> 00:11:44.900
you'll want to destroy the entire world for the absurdity you believe in, won't you?

00:11:44.900 --> 00:11:48.190
Whatever is necessary, we will do it

00:11:48.190 --> 00:11:50.163
with...with total commitment.  There

00:11:50.163 --> 00:11:51.788
is no other purpose.

00:11:51.788 --> 00:11:55.525
The purpose of life is to live and live fully.

00:11:55.525 --> 00:11:59.290
Living fully doesn't mean partying every night.

00:12:01.760 --> 00:12:03.986
Living fully means that

00:12:03.986 --> 00:12:07.498
before you die, you have explored every aspect of life;

00:12:07.498 --> 00:12:10.133
nothing has been left unexplored.  Yes

00:12:10.133 --> 00:12:11.561
?

00:12:11.561 --> 00:12:16.157
Before you die, even if you haven't explored the cosmos,

00:12:16.157 --> 00:12:19.821
at least you must have fully known this side of life.

00:12:19.821 --> 00:12:22.902
At least do that for yourself, right?

00:12:22.902 --> 00:12:27.076
This means living totally, experiencing this whole,

00:12:27.076 --> 00:12:29.662
this whole in all its dimensions.

00:12:29.662 --> 00:12:33.338
You left nothing untouched.  Just do this

00:12:33.338 --> 00:12:34.695
.  It will take you a

00:12:34.695 --> 00:12:36.573
long time.

00:12:36.573 --> 00:12:40.018
It's...a goal enough for you.

99:59:59.999 --> 100:00:05.999


